#EXPLOSIVE I
on block break:
	if player is (whatever you ned)
		loop blocks in radius 1 of event-block:
			if loop-block is cobblestone or coal_block or diamond_block or emerald_block or gold_block or iron_block or obsidian or any ore:
				add loop-block to {_explosive.%player%::*}
				loop {_explosive.%player%::*}:
					drop loop-value
					set loop-block to air
